snippet.title: Slow Pitch Jigging Rod Review "Pro Jigger" Jigging Amber Jacks
snippet.description:
Slow Pitch Jigging Rod Review "Pro Jigger"
The Johnny Jigs crew heads offshore with Jose Ramon. Jose is a slow pitch jigging enthusiast and a well known tournament bill fishermen. Will lands a nice amber jack and we dig deep into the New Pro Jigger slow pitch rod. Last but not least we head over to RJ Boyles Studio to stock the shelves and film a 4 part series for his fishing channel.

Pro Jigger Link
https://johnnyjigs.com/collections/rods-reels/products/johnnyjigs-graphite-slow-pitch-rod-70

Jigs Used In Video
Amber Jack Jig
https://johnnyjigs.com/collections/high-speed-knife-jigs/products/vertical-speed-jig-torpedo-blue-white-glow-200g

Mutton Snaper Jig
